cts.1.5","text":"For John truly baptized with water; but ye shall be baptized with the Holy Ghost not many days hence.","year":33},{"id":"recLaw4MFJzvwFN27","ref":"Acts.1.6","text":"When they therefore were come together, they asked of him, saying, Lord, wilt thou at this time restore again the kingdom to Israel?","year":33},{"id":"recbmUEowObFIvQgn","ref":"Acts.1.7","text":"And he said unto them, It is not for you to know the times or the seasons, which the Father hath put in his own power.","year":33},{"id":"rec9yuhy3ZyGmWh8C","ref":"Acts.1.8","text":"But ye shall receive power, after that the Holy Ghost is come upon you: and ye shall be witnesses unto me both in Jerusalem, and in all Judaea, and in Samaria, and unto the uttermost part of the earth.","year":33}]}
